{"tid":1164101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身體碰撞起爭執 兩男子被毆至頭破血流","createTime":"2019-05-21T00:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T00:40:41.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f355a57b8c7cfaf9b0e27554a505ec29d796ae81","tid":1164101,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9LXVF3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9LXVF3.png&h=92d2c526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣道與大南西街交界，一間便利店對開，凌晨1時許，兩名男子疑因身體碰撞問題與一名男子爭執後，遭對方持一米長的鐵鈎毆打，兩人不敵，身上有酒氣姓陳61歲男子被打傷耳及頭部，同行姓李49歲男子沿大南西街逃走至百米外，但被對方追及狂毆，致頭破血流受傷，逞兇者傷人後四散逃去，救護員到場將兩傷者送院治理，行人路遺下血迹，警員封鎖現場進行調查。"},{"pid":"49c872d062e089eb971d16cbde6bb972785eb723","tid":1164101,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人不敵</span>"},{"pid":"f54eed0a3a1e8f84fe80f188fe93f1b1be45ac00","tid":1164101,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"四散逃去？<br />\n<br />\n行凶者得一個人點四散"},{"pid":"b9beb4922008dda137daab9cabafb3fcc93acbc2","tid":1164101,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c872d062e089eb971d16cbde6bb972785eb723","tid":1164101,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人不敵</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"人地鐵鈎船長呀"},{"pid":"7d11e01ab0133ae85df848d814371bef01796bfb","tid":1164101,"uid":6378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9beb4922008dda137daab9cabafb3fcc93acbc2","tid":1164101,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c872d062e089eb971d16cbde6bb972785eb723","tid":1164101,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人不敵</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:30:42.000Z","msg":